" Something is sustainable if you can carry on doing it indefinitely . 

If you ca n't - it is n't . 

" Jonathan Porritt . 

Porritts definition implies that Mile End Park should be self-perpetuating and yet modern parks are a complex entity . 

There has been a real struggle to apply concepts of sustainability to the park 's development . 

The results can be demonstrated in three key areas : 1. Sustainability and design The idea of a sustainable urban park has been a key part of the design of Mile End Park . 

